{"tid":1345881,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如何用雨傘保護自己","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T04:10:34.000Z","uid":34275,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"28d1bf21541acbfd04cc342309209eb73f147cf9","tid":1345881,"uid":34275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:00:12.000Z","msg":"見到大家咁樣用把遮喺度敲敲敲，有啲嘢想講一下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NxprcxN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNxprcxN.jpg&h=f0d3dde7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一把遮最有用嘅部分其實係個頭<br />\n<br />\n要保護自己，保護家人，需要嘅係停止施襲者繼續。</span><br />\n<br />\n大家可以參考一下<br />\n<br />\nbayonet drill/刺槍術的方法<br />\n<br />\n簡介<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mobile01.com/topicdetail.php?f=37&amp;t=3918240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mobile01.com%2Ftopicdetail.php%3Ff%3D37%26t%3D3918240&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=fc604247\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mobile01.com/topicdetail.php?f=37&amp;t=3918240</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各地方法<br />\nUS<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oRNaL8ltlWs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoRNaL8ltlWs&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=946916ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oRNaL8ltlWs</a><br />\n<br />\n或者近少少<br />\n中華民國<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WIWx4IMY5hM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWIWx4IMY5hM&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=c3c3f562\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WIWx4IMY5hM</a><br />\n<br />\n其他人打你需要上而下揮舞<br />\n只要你用bayonet drill/刺槍術方法<br />\n行直線，就一定會比佢快。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">就算你只學到刺呢一下都足夠自保。</span><br />\n畢竟最有效嘅防守永遠都會係進攻。<br />\n<br />\n祝大家出入平安<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Ps 這是一項體育運動</span>"},{"pid":"127f78e99a6be26929a4b945077d78522785070f","tid":1345881,"uid":28257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"屌遮冇撚用嫁，唔長唔短，除左擋椒有咩用，打人又唔夠長，防又唔夠硬<br />\n<br />\n都唔明成日拎遮做乜春，"},{"pid":"de6a29e772897493070e5caab0e6855d2a662673","tid":1345881,"uid":34275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:08:46.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"dc9fe2f70d3590f0452d0a0d9588cfbb3656cb0d","tid":1345881,"uid":34275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"ec4c2a3ea35aeb98343e6c539806217b9f520c62","tid":1345881,"uid":34275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"9424d22c518522ffba682a57e6140a32f7254102","tid":1345881,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"遮有用，白衫個班就拎曬遮啦"},{"pid":"d72f314c0449111e36681b604e0f9a2107f7c0dd","tid":1345881,"uid":34275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:09:19.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"5d2be0df183caee1b67f01ed37be891a59c3a8e2","tid":1345881,"uid":34275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"127f78e99a6be26929a4b945077d78522785070f","tid":1345881,"uid":28257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"屌遮冇撚用嫁，唔長唔短，除左擋椒有咩用，打人又唔夠長，防又唔夠硬<br />\n<br />\n都唔明成日拎遮做乜春，"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:10:32.000Z","msg":"用嚟刺架<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">敲無用架<br />\n敲無用架<br />\n敲無用架<br />\n敲無用架<br />\n敲無用架</span>"},{"pid":"e1fb2354ba4c80f71a311d2a66573975704e1797","tid":1345881,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d2be0df183caee1b67f01ed37be891a59c3a8e2","tid":1345881,"uid":34275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"127f78e99a6be26929a4b945077d78522785070f","tid":1345881,"uid":28257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"屌遮冇撚用嫁，唔長唔短，除左擋椒有咩用，打人又唔夠長，防又唔夠硬<br />\n<br />\n都唔明成日拎遮做乜春，"},"citedBy":1,"reply